</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub65.ezboard.com/ulananirigger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>lananirigger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 53<br> <font color=#993300>(3/1/02 12:32:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/femarr80492frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=145.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Clerics and Non-Clerics...  Opinion please...</span><hr size=1> OK here we go.....MA/and Puller need it! as for the casters.....<br>
lets see here  i know for a fact that NECROs get DMG absorb Spells, AND have Harmshield...STEELSKIN for a necro requires a Jasper (i think it is, i have it and use it) good for about 250dmg...DIAMOND SKIN requires guess what  (PERIDOT) good for about 400dmg....if the wittle necro behaves in a manner that is not congurent to a long and prosporous life and requires a Symobol.. that wittle necro can give up one of his/her gems to have said protection.... now here comes the smack in the face.... ENCHANTERS!!!!!!!! u get rune spells  same as the Skin spells the necros have, and YES they require a gem.....if the Echie that can make tons of cash with the jewelcrafting is so inclined to beg every 5 seconds for a symbol, he/she might think about giving up one of the gems they have for RUNE to the chanter...<br>
<br>
hehe now dont go jumping down my throat..i know chanters are needed in many high lvl dungeons and playing in OS has taught me one think,  CHANTERS get Smacked around....Clerics get Phat Loots in Gems....and the NECRO is always looking for a group....<br>
<br>
